Singer, Ayo Balogun, widely referred to as Wizkid has recently been announced as the winner of the Artiste of the Year in the 14th edition of the 2021 Headies award. The father of three emerged the winner of this category following keen contest from other notable names on the list. The artist of the year category comprises: Headies award were reported to have sent a private jet to Ghana to pick Wizkid up for the event on Sunday evening. One of Africa’s biggest and most decorated artistes released “Made in Lagos” last year, which in less than four months won Wizkid the award.